r 实体店在新泽西州开业时，唐纳森及其团队到场，到场<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.bonappetit.com/story/mrbeast-burger-restaurant-opening">人数超过 10,000 人</a>。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/mrbeasts-burger-company-countersues-the-youtube-megastar-for-over-100-million-183859754.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/mrbeasts-burger-company-countersues-the-youtube-megastar-for-over-100-million-183859754.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> a0f88294-6a9c-4ea7-bffc-4336b572fcdb</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 07 Aug 2023 18:38:59 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691442607</ingested><modified> 2023-08-07T21:10:15+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="2573" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/47b02a00-354f-11ee-b94e-80d568286f7d" width="3600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2573" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/47b02a00-354f-11ee-b94e-80d568286f7d" width="3600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Dave Kotinsky via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[EAST RUTHERFORD, NEW JERSEY - SEPTEMBER 04: (L-R) Nolan Hansen, Sapnap, MrBeast, Karl Jacob